summary: An ordinance providing for the payment of the cost and expense of the laying off, extending and establishing of Kenyon Street, and providing for the condemnation, appropriation, taking and damaging of land and other property necessary therefor, under Ordinance No. and levying and assessing the amounts thereof against the several lots, tracts, parcels of land and other property as shown on said roll, establishing a Local Improvement Fund. Ordinance No. 30315 of the City of Seattle, by the issuance and sale of the bonds of the district created to pay therefor.
